\c 143
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti Jehovha achimbidzike kumurwira
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Inzwai munyengetero wangu, Jehovha; teererai kukumbira kwangu; Ndipindurei nokutendeka kwenyu nokururama kwenyu.
\p
\v 2 Regai kutonga muranda wenyu; Nokuti hapana munhu mumwe mupenyu
\s angaruramiswa pamberi penyu.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti muvengi akatambudza mweya wangu;
\s Akatsikirira upenyu hwangu pasi; Akandigarisa panzvimbo dzine rima, savanhu vakanguva vafa.
\p
\v 4 Saka mweya wangu wavhunduswa mukati mangu.
\s Mwoyo wangu wavhunduswa mukati mangu.
\p
\v 5 Ndinorangarira mazuva akare; Ndinofungisisa zvose zvamakaita; Ndinofunga basa ramaoko enyu.
\p
\v 6 Ndinotambanudzira maoko angu kwamuri;
\s Mweya wangu unokushuvai
\s senyika yakaomerwa.
\p
\v 7 Kurumidzai kupindura, Jehovha; mweya wangu waziya;
\s Regai kundivanzira chiso chenyu; Ndigosava savanoburukira kugomba.
\p
\v 8 Ndinzwisei unyoro hwenyu mangwanani;
\s Nokuti ndinovimba nemi;
\s Ndizivisei nzira yandinofanira kufamba nayo;
\s Nokuti ndinosimudzira mweya wangu kwamuri.
\p
\v 9 Ndirwirei Jehovha, panavavengi vangu;
\s Ndinovanda nemi.
\p
\v 1 Â° Ndidzidzisei kuita kuda kwenyu; nokuti ndimi Mwari wangu; Mweya wenyu, wakanaka
\s ngaundifambise
\s munyika yakati chechetere,
\p
\v 11 Ndiponesei Jehovha, nokuda kwezita renyu;
\s Budisai mweya wangu pakumanikidzwa nokururama kwenyu.
\p
\v 12 Pedzai vavengi vangu nounyoro hwenyu,
\s Muparadze vose vanomanikidza mweya wangu;
\s Nokuti ndiri muranda wenyu.
